<emphasis id="D8AE8330FFC2FFD5FF14E96D067B2D3A" bold="true" box="[151,272,1042,1068]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="560">Euscyrtus</emphasis>
Guerin-Meneville, 1844
