<paragraph id="EA655F22FFC2FFD5FF14E92902F82D78" blockId="1.[151,1427,1110,1134]" box="[151,1427,1110,1134]" pageId="1" pageNumber="560">Guerin-Meneville, 1844. Icon. R. anim. Ins: 334. Gorochov, 1988. Trudy Zool. Inst., Akad. Nauk SSSR, Leningrad 178:3â€“31.</paragraph>
